	<!-- Contraband Smuggler (Constable) -->
	<Language_en_US>
		<Row Tag="TXT_KEY_CITY_EVENT_CONTRABAND_SMUGGLERS_DESCRIPTION">
			<Text>Black Market</Text>
		</Row>
		<Row Tag="TXT_KEY_CITY_EVENT_CONTRABAND_SMUGGLERS_HELP">
			<Text>The authorities have intercepted a small scale operation smuggling contraband into the city.[NEWLINE][NEWLINE]The Governor thinks they might be of use...</Text>
		</Row>
		<Row Tag="TXT_KEY_CITY_EVENT_CONTRABAND_SMUGGLERS_HELP_CHOICE_1">
			<Text>Gain {2_InstantYield}.</Text>
		</Row>
		<Row Tag="TXT_KEY_CITY_EVENT_CONTRABAND_SMUGGLERS_HELP_CHOICE_2">
			<Text>Lose {2_InstantYield} Golden Age Points. The threshold for [ICON_STRENGTH] Crime is permentantly reduced by 10%.</Text>
		</Row>
		<Row Tag="TXT_KEY_CITY_EVENT_CONTRABAND_SMUGGLERS_HELP_CHOICE_3">
			<Text>The Constabulary gains +2 [ICON_PRODUCTION] Production.</Text>
		</Row>
		<Row Tag="TXT_KEY_CITY_EVENT_CONTRABAND_SMUGGLERS_HELP_CHOICE_4">
			<Text>Gain 10 turns of WLTKD in the city.</Text>
		</Row>
		<Row Tag="TXT_KEY_CITY_EVENT_CONTRABAND_SMUGGLERS_DESCRIPTION_CHOICE_1">
			<Text>No deals. The law is clear on their punishment.</Text>
		</Row>
		<Row Tag="TXT_KEY_CITY_EVENT_CONTRABAND_SMUGGLERS_DESCRIPTION_CHOICE_2">
			<Text>Talk of corruption in my very presence?! I am the law. Find me a new Governor, and hang the old one beside these criminals.</Text>
		</Row>
		<Row Tag="TXT_KEY_CITY_EVENT_CONTRABAND_SMUGGLERS_DESCRIPTION_CHOICE_3">
			<Text>I agree. There will always be crime; it would be useful to have friends on the other side of the law.</Text>
		</Row>
		<Row Tag="TXT_KEY_CITY_EVENT_CONTRABAND_SMUGGLERS_DESCRIPTION_CHOICE_4">
			<Text>Banning these goods is, I think, a little old-fashioned. Pardon the smugglers and legalise these products.</Text>
		</Row>
	</Language_en_US>
